HEADWORD: Lacedæmonian
<hw>Lac`e*d⟦ae⟧*mo"ni*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>Lacedamonius</ets>, Gr. <grk>Lakedaimo`nios</grk>, fr.
<grk>Lakedai`mwn</grk> Laced⟦ae⟧mon.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to
